{"tid":1174773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重溫]  超霸氣！美國安顧問：中國再海上挑釁就走交戰規則","createTime":"2019-05-28T05:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T10:53:48.000Z","uid":141151,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a5809f3eabd623557d262bde351d1aa759a0f97d","tid":1174773,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:41:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2584143\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2584143&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=731ca7ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2584143&h=47c995ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2584143</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://freebeacon.com/national-security/bolton-warns-chinese-military-halt-dangerous-naval-encounters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffreebeacon.com%2Fnational-security%2Fbolton-warns-chinese-military-halt-dangerous-naval-encounters&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=33ba5d05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://freebeacon.com/national-security/bolton-warns-chinese-military-halt-dangerous-naval-encounters</a><br />\n<br />\n超霸氣！美國安顧問：中國再海上挑釁就走交戰規則<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國驅逐艦狄卡特號（USS Decatur）9月30日航行在南海海域，未料中國解放軍艦「蘭州號」衝來，差點造成兩艦碰撞；美國白宮國家安全顧問波頓（John Bolton）近期內對此指出，若中國再挑釁，戰艦指揮官就按交戰規則處理。<br />\n<br />\n根據《華盛頓自由燈塔》報導，波頓接受電台評論員休．修伊特（Hugh Hewitt）專訪時表明，「我們不會容忍威脅美國軍人的舉動，我們決心要讓公海航線保持開放，這是中國人需要了解的事情，他們的長期以來的行為一直是不必要的挑釁」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">波頓警告中國，美國海軍戰艦上的指揮官必須保護戰艦，這些指揮官在遭遇緊急情況時是被允許進入交戰狀態的，他重複強調「指揮官擁有我們需要的權力」。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n波頓11日曾在推特上表明，他在10月為促進美國在安全上的利益，將開啟出訪行程；外媒透露，波頓預計於本月20日抵達俄羅斯，並在24日造訪西亞國家亞塞拜然，接著還要去亞美尼亞與東歐國家喬治亞；據悉，這些國家都與中國「一帶一路」計畫有關。"},{"pid":"b23d87a4290376c911269ca38fc7313ca41de23a","tid":1174773,"uid":35430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:42:04.000Z","msg":"支那；我一向唔守規則"},{"pid":"633b335b696653a02342b208bf913687c1e4fc29","tid":1174773,"uid":41428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"已經係上年既新聞<br />\nOctober 12, 2018"},{"pid":"72fd10cf14f7650a057b01a809316fe621589c0c","tid":1174773,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d215434443f478b07474c8a368f6dc5f515a71ca","tid":1174773,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T06:38:55.000Z","msg":"what is the Roe?"},{"pid":"934314841c0acadc733561a6d1868b4796fb6301","tid":1174773,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T06:42:10.000Z","msg":"仲以為個顧問姓安，原來係安全顧問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe4c0335143d7dd3abb6dc2bd2095330826d45f","tid":1174773,"uid":150347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:36:40.000Z","msg":"標題咪寫左重溫囉，樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3253828d154f97da135579e80dfed3cafbd023f6","tid":1174773,"uid":195570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:51:39.000Z","msg":"一陣習總派幾隻漁船撞沉你啊"},{"pid":"f725a712093a886db2ca92cd299f448be5ebe3ba","tid":1174773,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d215434443f478b07474c8a368f6dc5f515a71ca","tid":1174773,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T06:38:55.000Z","msg":"what is the Roe?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"Shoot to kill"}]}